    "Each of the models covered in this study has its own merits and demerits.",
    "Additionally, each model has been shown to perform well in a variety of image segmentation tasks.",
    "In this paper, Mi et al.",
    "evaluate the efficiency of WCE in detecting polyps using AI models like DL, a meta-analysis was carried out because the full studies had small-size samples and various algorithms (Mi et al. 2022).",
    "For possibly suitable research published up to December 8, 2021, the search was conducted by two independent reviewers using Embase, the Cochrane Library, PubMed, and, the Web of Science."
